TLofIf-mc012KAkrmgP8kj8u3aqyN2GGKBDY9OsQq=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2019-07-26T16:32:54.227453Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNVNFp2bUZ3EAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNVNFp2bUZ3EAE!2m1!1s0x80857c2f50ecd20b:0x679f6d33cd0e7f17"}, {"name": "places/ChIJC9LsUC98hYARF38OzTNtn2c/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WUU5GUmliWEpZZFdkRWNIbEhlV2N3UWtaTWVrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "From the variety of moon cake, to their sponge cake almond, to the variety of breads and all the way to the other pastries I loved this little hidden gem inside a Chinese market mall.\n\nEverything was so cheap and all the pastries we took home were amazing but only one thing they need to improve is the lady charging you. So rude towards my family! Just because they didn’t understand something she said, come on they’re 70ish and 90ish. She has to learn some patience!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "From the variety of moon cake, to their sponge cake almond, to the variety of breads and all the way to the other pastries I loved this little hidden gem inside a Chinese market mall.\n\nEverything was so cheap and all the pastries we took home were amazing but only one thing they need to improve is the lady charging you. So rude towards my family! Just because they didn’t understand something she said, come on they’re 70ish and 90ish. She has to learn some patience!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cindy C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103176060795846415103/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3WEvl7tcBvN-ZKSN9HPT_moD81oSBB_IiQzfK2eetM44WWK-1oA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-26T08:15:02.289237196Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/co